cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with attacks and defenses against deep neural network classifiers for image ranking systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves designing an objective function, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). As the paper deals with adversarial attacks, it could also be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper involves designing attacks and defenses using optimization techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves evaluating the attacks and defenses on datasets, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
